pulses.name: 20240808 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
08 Aug 2024 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Attacks:

- Multiple Routers GPON formLogin Remote Command Injection - A prevalent vulnerability exploited by attackers to gain unauthorized access to router configurations.
- NETGEAR DGN1000 CGI Unauthenticated Remote Code Execution - This attack allows unauthorized command execution on NETGEAR devices, posing significant security risks.
- SystemBC Botnet - A common threat that facilitates various malicious activities, including data theft and system compromise.
